author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Ominto Inc Announces Voluntary Delisting From Nasdaq Stock Market
text:
May 14 (Reuters) - Ominto Inc:
* OMINTO, INC. ANNOUNCES VOLUNTARY DELISTING FROM THE NASDAQ STOCK MARKET
* OMINTO INC - ANTICIPATED THAT DELISTING WILL BECOME EFFECTIVE JUNE 3, 2018
* OMINTO INC - EXPECTS LAST DAY OF TRADING OF ITS COMMON STOCK ON NASDAQ CAPITAL MARKET WILL BE ON OR ABOUT JUNE 1, 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
